{"tid":1910711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國眾議院通過「台北法案」協助台灣鞏固邦交、參與國際組織並增強雙方經貿關係","createTime":"2020-03-05T00:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T06:55:12.000Z","uid":125168,"like":469,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"1022652eb291b449eef9e086c315da4fc7d9c7ea","tid":1910711,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:23:28.000Z","msg":"美國眾議院通過「台北法案」促增強雙方關係<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院通過「台北法案」，要求美國行政部門協助台灣鞏固邦交、參與國際組織並增強雙方經貿關係。眾議院在415票贊成、無人投反對票下通過法案。根據法案，美國行政部門在適當並符合美國外交政策利益下，對嚴重傷害台灣安全或繁榮的國家，應該考慮改變有關經濟、安全及外交接觸。眾議院通過的法案，是早前經參議院通過後的修正版本，需要送回參議院再表決，通過後遞交總統特朗普簽署生效。<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-05 08:15:40 rthk tg"},{"pid":"4b67b6ac8db0baee8e8873643435a84c248b0c0c","tid":1910711,"uid":125168,"like":122,"dislike":2,"score":120,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HzXH7Ke.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzXH7Ke.jpg&h=bfea39a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7d3730689f3526c7ac91896af32c4bbde8fecaa","tid":1910711,"uid":3113,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:24:46.000Z","msg":"taiwan no1"},{"pid":"63ab7eb551c4aa5b122784d9d780df320ea11873","tid":1910711,"uid":125168,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"b7d3730689f3526c7ac91896af32c4bbde8fecaa","tid":1910711,"uid":3113,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:24:46.000Z","msg":"taiwan no1"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:25:35.000Z","msg":"台灣有美國已經包無死，好羡慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0253d2dc8827ca20e1fc212caed89474d6717a2","tid":1910711,"uid":125168,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T00:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TYtwgDs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTYtwgDs.gif&h=ee1b6a05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28c9efb4961d4b11a499ef4c6e76caa0b8326e49","tid":1910711,"uid":263618,